('063aa8ec-0b55-5d81-8949-4563026b960f', 3, 'solo_rpls_no_successor', 'positive', NULL, 'TBPELS firm roster + RPLS cross-reference shows exactly 1 active RPLS at firm #10071100 (MARVIN WILLIAM REAVIS) — no second RPLS added in 46yr tenure. No credentialed internal successor visible at the license-board level. NOTE: live team-page fetch required before A-tier promotion per skill non-negotiable.', 'tbpels_firm_rpls_join', 'https://tbpedownloads.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/rpls_roster.csv', '2026-05-16'),
